<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ثُمَّ اسْتَثْنَى فَقَالَ:</span> <span class="c3">{إِلا الَّذِينَ آمنُوا وَعمِلُوا الصَّالِحَات}</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ قَتَادَةُ:</span> اسْتَثْنَى اللَّهُ الشُّعَرَاءَ مِنَ الْمُؤْمِنِينَ؛<span class="c5"> مِنْهُمْ:</span> حَسَّانُ بْنُ ثَابِتٍ،<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>